text:
<!channel> Hi again! To reiterate what was discussed in lecture tonight:
1. Please make resume edits ASAP. You can expect round 2 suggestions by January 19. If you do not have your edits done when I open it, I will skip and come back after I am done with the rest of the resumes. 
2. Interview Day 2 is Monday, January 15. You will be notified by class on Monday if you did not pass. 
3. If you have re-scoping questions due to fewer team members, please reach out to Colin, Lexi, your TA, and myself and we can help you game plan!
Home stretch! You all have got this!
